===Verb===
{{en-verb|seugues|segueing|segued|segued}}

# To move [[smoothly]] from one state or subject to another.
#: ''She '''segued''' from our conversation about school to the topic of marriage.''
#{{music}} To make a smooth [[transition]] from one theme to another.
#: ''Beethoven's symphonies effortlessly '''segue''' from one theme to the next.''
#(''of a disk jockey'') To play a [[sequence]] of [[record]]s with no [[talk]] between them.

